{"tid":1884576,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[遊記] 搭車又搭船之陸路遊俄羅斯烏克蘭","createTime":"2020-02-17T16:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T05:22:14.000Z","uid":145405,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"633175d6adda7fb4b6b121be171d417d6813b523","tid":1884576,"uid":145405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:24:36.000Z","msg":"因為呢排太得閒，睇返啲相，就順便將成個旅行統整下。因為覺得人一世物一世又懶係慳錢咁，揀左係北京搭巴士入蒙古，再由蒙古一路搭火車去莫斯科。之不過，其實之後都唔慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始問個司機要搭幾耐，佢話12個鐘會到，最後搭左22個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。因為行下停下，半夜仲會停埋路邊瞓到天光先再開車。本身我地坐車頭好窄嘅位，好彩問下司機之後比我地改個闊啲嘅位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7y9Qhu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7y9Qhu.jpg&h=b4d99d5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HEsKEa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHEsKEa0.jpg&h=9707b876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到二連浩特過關，然後再上返同一架車去扎門烏德。係過關途中遇到幾個中國大叔，佢地係咁偷望我地本passport，唔覺唔覺開始吹水講佢地簽證要幾多錢咁。<br />\n<br />\n終於捱過左巴士之旅，之後就係時候要上火車。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUN6Svf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUN6Svf.jpg&h=3c205ed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地係去到扎門烏德先買車飛，其實本身都驚溝通唔到，但發現有幾個同我地同巴士嘅後生仔係識中文，咁就揾到幫手買車飛。因為呢件事，識埋個蒙古妹妹，仲一齊食飯同係火車度吹水。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最得人驚係我地又撞返個幾個中國大叔，仲話要揾我地一齊去食飯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BRRfLSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBRRfLSa.jpg&h=2786a7ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YtgLoDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYtgLoDU.jpg&h=986268ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都算係環境最惡劣嘅一程火車，隔離係蒙古大媽，呢個蒙古大媽又敷mask ，又化妝，又話我地嘈，但真係好沖擊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我地搭1805嘅車，所以瞓醒就落車啦，唔捨得蒙古妹妹。一落車落狗屎，成條馬路水浸咁，無辦法之下嘅辦法係企係條街截車。老老竇竇我都分唔到邊啲係的士，求其有車開門比我地就上。好彩都醒醒目目咁講左價先上車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DqtxN7W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDqtxN7W.jpg&h=9ca400d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁就出發去酒店，一開始個司機都揾唔到，佢拉低窗求其揾人問，最後終於到酒店啦。係時候去醫肚啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLrGGtQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLrGGtQ.jpg&h=b72ad83c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n酒店入面聲稱係韓燒嘅餐廳，但係啲牛係蒙古牛同埋係yak。捱左咁耐，終於可以嘆下啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vx7uQou.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvx7uQou.jpg&h=799cfe0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jp6Wvox.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJp6Wvox.jpg&h=d16d8ffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打住先"},{"pid":"141700e104e95ba522882e3d4bcf949455ae557d","tid":1884576,"uid":56209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"留名 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7765b7f864924485ae4d7acb00e3ceff5dbe6b","tid":1884576,"uid":145405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"係蒙古住左一晚，就要上火車去伊爾庫茨克。車飛係好似係扎門烏德個度買埋嘅，但得返頭等，結果就搭上左頭等車之旅。<br />\n<br />\n臨上火車前有段小插曲，就係我地唔夠錢搭的士。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講極價都無我地去酒店個陣咁平仲要貴好多。最後係唔知點算嘅情況底下，企左係間酒店門口。咁啱有個的士司機係度，本身都話唔得架，最後唔知係咪見我地太慘，所以唔夠錢都載我地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRbrWEr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRbrWEr.jpg&h=38b1b87a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sznboju.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsznboju.jpg&h=87d16338&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NwMjxcS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNwMjxcS.jpg&h=5f7598ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sh9X3jA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSh9X3jA.jpg&h=be67932b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bgKMWEC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbgKMWEC.jpg&h=7f7f7a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為係由蒙古過境去俄羅斯嘅車，所以半夜係會比人叫醒，有海關帶埋隻狗逐卡逐卡睇passport同睇你。<br />\n<br />\n終於到左，又係陰天同落雨。<br />\n<br />\n呢座喀山聖母大教堂係俄羅斯第3靚嘅教堂，同埋個度條街真係無乜人，又因為陰天嘅關係，帶點荒涼嘅感覺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/agGoetv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FagGoetv.jpg&h=4085fffa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bdo9Utz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdo9Utz.jpg&h=fd20e321&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9nY9UtD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9nY9UtD.jpg&h=097bdf04&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z46WztH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz46WztH.jpg&h=b6eb5f2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個度搭巴士都好傳統，車上面會有個工人負責收錢。你上左車，佢等陣就會過嚟問你拎錢。其實去得呢度，都要去埋貝加爾湖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2xSF1dn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2xSF1dn.jpg&h=c9364b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特登上網揾過資料，係市場個度有好多車都係去奧爾洪島，因為我地無一早買定車飛或者book定，慎防意外生，影低定個電話號碼有咩事都揾到車呱。<br />\n<br />\n最後我地提早一日買飛，佢會比張細細嘅卡紙，然後第二朝個司機會直接去酒店接我地。好得意個司機係會係whatsapp聯絡，本身佢前一晚都未聯絡我地都淆淆地，好彩有電話號碼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zePX3tX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzePX3tX.jpg&h=287491b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KvrGLHj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKvrGLHj.jpg&h=d6cb32d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYRjxnn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYRjxnn.jpg&h=fd78044f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zf67GfL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZf67GfL.jpg&h=d9fc5e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢鑊真係搭車又搭船。由市區去奧爾洪島差唔多搭左4個幾鐘，本身以為架船泊埋岸就到，點知去住嘅地方都坐左個幾鐘車。 所以夾埋我地又搭左6個鐘車啦。<br />\n<br />\n同車有個韓國叔叔，佢跟住我地落車，本身以為唔通佢book埋同我地同一間?! 點知原來佢係無book到仼何野就走左入島，個host都話full晒，佢就默默離開左，唔知佢最後點呢。係木屋仔個度識左一班大媽加個阿叔加個女。個大叔同個女識俄文，之後完全就係跟住佢地係個度玩。查實俄羅斯真係好多大陸人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGWPacX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGWPacX.jpg&h=1359110c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zCAHvc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCAHvc0.jpg&h=b1983895&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L06vD6o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL06vD6o.jpg&h=17b998ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F32rcrr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF32rcrr.jpg&h=02da081a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A7mvD6t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7mvD6t.jpg&h=b1083d96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xA32vda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxA32vda.jpg&h=19bbc2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLYNGjU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLYNGjU.jpg&h=f7f6c5f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夏天嘅貝加爾湖，就好似成個海咁。去貝加爾湖有分南線北線。我唔記得左邊條長啲，但因為一定要包車玩，所以多啲人係化算啲，如果唔係，我估木屋仔個host都會幫你拼車。個邊啲路好顛簸，基本上你想係車度瞓覺係無可能嘅事。因為同行阿叔識俄文，佢會叫司機帶我地去啲無咁多人嘅地方望湖。仲有，包車係包埋晏晝飯，其實真係幾舒服。<br />\n<br />\n有啲地方仲會見到有人露營，其實真係可以揾個草地攤一日，望下天望下湖，遠離下。下次再去，我會想冬天去睇下。<br />\n<br />\n基本上，住左兩晚又要搭返6個鐘頭車出返去。出返伊爾庫茨克都係又係睇下教堂，行下商場，行下河邊，賣懶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6MtJY9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6MtJY9Z.jpg&h=ecd585ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GDLMcu2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGDLMcu2.jpg&h=6347d1a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQNnvgL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQNnvgL.jpg&h=c03e8671&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YT7F1ot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYT7F1ot.jpg&h=676de9dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Si3YN3w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSi3YN3w.jpg&h=d6acdef0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}